Package: SMED
Type: Package
Title: Sequential Minimum Energy Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Collin Erickson
Maintainer: Collin Erickson <collinberickson@gmail.com>
Description: Selects points sequentially that are spaced out according to
    an energy function. It is good for picking points that balance 
    space-filling and focuses in on an objective.
License: GPL-3
